The paper also discusses the use of a hybrid automaton and a phase-space metric, which are topics related to control systems and system theory, respectively. Therefore, cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also a likely sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of planning and control algorithms, which are topics related to artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of simulations, which are topics related to machine learning and computer vision. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) are also possible sub-categories.
